  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "This version of Who Wants To Be A Millionaire was released on Wii and DS in 2010.\n\nPlayers try to answer 15 multiple-choice questions of increasing difficulty, with the dollar value for each question increasing all the way up to one million dollars. If they player is stumped by a question, they may narrow their choices down by using up one of three lifelines - Ask the Audience, Double Dip, and Phone a Friend. Players can also choose to walk away and retain their winnings.",
